---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container fade-up">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Our story</span>
    <h1>Built for the care women<br>have always deserved.</h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub">Behold Your Wonder® exists because the system wasn't working. Not for women. Not for their bodies. Not for the complexity of their lives.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-grid fade-up">
      <div>
        <span class="story-label">Why we exist</span>
        <div class="story-text">
          <p>Women have spent years being told their symptoms are stress, or anxiety, or just part of being a woman. They have sat in waiting rooms, filled out intake forms, and been handed referrals that led nowhere. They have been seen by specialists who treated one part of them while the rest went unaddressed.</p>
          <p>What they did not get — what most women never get — is a place that understands that the mind and the body are not separate systems. That PMDD, postpartum anxiety, fertility grief, perimenopause, thyroid disruption, and the weight of simply being a woman in the world are all connected. That your care should be too.</p>
          <p>Behold Your Wonder was built to change that. Not generic therapy adapted for women. Not a wellness platform light on clinical rigor. A real clinical environment designed specifically for the hormonal, emotional, and relational complexity of women's lives.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="story-img-wrap">
          <img src="/all_women.jpg" alt="Women of all backgrounds served at Behold Your Wonder" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;border-radius:var(--radius-lg)">
        </div>
        <p class="photo-credit">Photo by <a href="https://www.instagram.com/anntarazevich" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anna Tarazevich</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mission">
  <div class="container fade-up">
    <p class="mission-quote">"You have spent years being told your symptoms are just anxiety, just stress, just part of it. We built Behold Your Wonder for the women who are ready to be cared for by people who understand that hormones and mental health are the same conversation."</p>
    <p class="mission-attr">— Salatha Helton, LMFT · Founder, Behold Your Wonder</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pillars">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pillars-head fade-up">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-dark">Clinical philosophy</span>
      <h2>The principles that guide<br>how we practice</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card fade-up"><div class="pillar-num">01</div><p class="pillar-title">Mind and body are one conversation</p><p class="pillar-desc">Hormonal health and mental health are inseparable. We treat them that way — not as separate specialties requiring separate appointments.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card fade-up"><div class="pillar-num">02</div><p class="pillar-title">Coordination is clinical care</p><p class="pillar-desc">Fragmented care isn't a logistics problem — it's a clinical one. Our infrastructure ensures every provider has the context they need to help you.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card fade-up"><div class="pillar-num">03</div><p class="pillar-title">Evidence-based, not trend-based</p><p class="pillar-desc">We draw on CBT, Psychodynamic, Humanistic, somatic approaches, and our proprietary CMBT modality. Rigorous methods, applied with warmth and specificity.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card fade-up"><div class="pillar-num">04</div><p class="pillar-title">Access between sessions matters</p><p class="pillar-desc">Life does not wait for your next appointment. Our async support model extends the therapeutic relationship beyond the hour.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card fade-up"><div class="pillar-num">05</div><p class="pillar-title">You are the expert on yourself</p><p class="pillar-desc">Our clinicians act as guides, not authorities. The therapeutic process is driven by your data, your insights, and your experience.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card fade-up"><div class="pillar-num">06</div><p class="pillar-title">Community is part of healing</p><p class="pillar-desc">Being witnessed by women navigating similar experiences has therapeutic value. Our group offerings are clinically structured and built for depth.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="diff">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="diff-head fade-up">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">The BYW difference</span>
      <h2>What care looks like<br>when it actually works</h2>
      <p>Most women have experienced fragmented care. Here's what changes when your providers are working together.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-grid fade-up">
      <div>
        <p class="diff-col-title">Fragmented care</p>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon bad"></div><p class="diff-text">Separate appointments with providers who don't communicate</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon bad"></div><p class="diff-text">Repeating your history to every new specialist</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon bad"></div><p class="diff-text">Therapists without hormonal health training</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon bad"></div><p class="diff-text">No support between sessions</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon bad"></div><p class="diff-text">Referrals that lead nowhere</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon bad"></div><p class="diff-text">Being told it's just anxiety</p></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="diff-col-title">Behold Your Wonder</p>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon good"></div><p class="diff-text">A coordinated clinical team working in concert</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon good"></div><p class="diff-text">One intake. Your context follows you.</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon good"></div><p class="diff-text">Clinicians selected for hormonal mental health expertise</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon good"></div><p class="diff-text">Async support between every session</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon good"></div><p class="diff-text">Warm handoffs to a vetted specialist network</p></div>
        <div class="diff-item"><div class="diff-icon good"></div><p class="diff-text">Care that connects the dots</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="founder">
  <div class="container fade-up">
    <div class="founder-card">
      <div class="founder-photo"><img src="/salatha_LMFT.jpg" alt="Salatha Helton, LMFT" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:var(--radius-md)"></div>
      <div>
        <p class="founder-name">Salatha Helton</p>
        <p class="founder-cred">LMFT · Founder & Clinical Director</p>
        <div class="founder-bio">
          <p>Salatha Helton is a Licensed Marriage and Family Therapist and the founder of Behold Your Wonder. Her clinical work is rooted in the belief that women's mental health cannot be separated from the hormonal and relational complexity of their lives.</p>
          <p>Salatha is the co-creator of Core Messaging Based Therapy (CMBT)™ — an integrative therapeutic approach that draws on psychodynamic theory, CBT, Emotionally Focused Therapy, and humanistic psychology.</p>
          <p>Behold Your Wonder was founded to build the clinical infrastructure that women have always needed — and never had.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-cta">
  <div class="container fade-up">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Ready to begin</span>
    <h2>This was built for you.</h2>
    <p>A 25-minute consultation with a specialist. No pressure, no commitment.</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a href="https://beholdyourwonder.clientsecure.me" class="btn-primary">Book a 25 minute consultation</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn-outline-light">See our services</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
.page-hero{background:var(--ink);padding:clamp(64px,10vw,110px) 0;text-align:center}
.page-hero h1{color:#fff;margin-bottom:18px}
.page-hero-sub{font-size:clamp(14px,1.8vw,16px);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);line-height:1.75;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto}

.story{background:var(--cream);padding:var(--pad) 0}
.story-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(40px,6vw,80px);align-items:center}
.story-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:14px;display:block}
.story-text{font-size:clamp(14px,1.6vw,16px);color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.85}
.story-text p+p{margin-top:16px}
.story-img-wrap{position:relative;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/5}
.photo-credit{text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:8px}
.photo-credit a{color:var(--gold-dk);text-decoration:underline}

.mission{background:var(--ink);padding:var(--pad) 0;text-align:center}
.mission-quote{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,34px);font-style:italic;color:#fff;line-height:1.45;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto 28px;font-weight:300}
.mission-attr{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);letter-spacing:0.06em}

.pillars{background:var(--cream);padding:var(--pad) 0}
.pillars-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:clamp(36px,5vw,56px)}
.pillars-head h2{color:var(--ink)}
.pillar-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:var(--gap)}
.pillar-card{background:#fff;border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:clamp(24px,3vw,36px)}
.pillar-num{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:44px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(245,184,0,0.35);line-height:1;margin-bottom:14px}
.pillar-title{font-size:clamp(14px,1.5vw,16px);font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:10px}
.pillar-desc{font-size:clamp(12px,1.3vw,13px);color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.75}

.diff{background:var(--ink);padding:var(--pad) 0}
.diff-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:clamp(36px,5vw,56px)}
.diff-head h2{color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px}
.diff-head p{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px}
.diff-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(32px,5vw,64px)}
.diff-col-title{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:24px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}
.diff-item{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-bottom:20px;align-items:flex-start}
.diff-icon{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:7px}
.diff-icon.bad{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15)}
.diff-icon.good{background:var(--gold)}
.diff-text{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,14px);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);line-height:1.65}

.founder{background:var(--cream);padding:var(--pad) 0}
.founder-card{background:#fff;border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:clamp(32px,4vw,52px);display:grid;grid-template-columns:200px 1fr;gap:clamp(28px,4vw,52px);align-items:start}
.founder-photo{background:var(--green-lt);border-radius:var(--radius-md);aspect-ratio:3/4;overflow:hidden}
.founder-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:4px;font-weight:300}
.founder-cred{font-size:12px;color:var(--gold-dk);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:20px}
.founder-bio{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,15px);color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.85}
.founder-bio p+p{margin-top:14px}

.about-cta{background:var(--gold);padding:var(--pad) 0;text-align:center}
.about-cta h2{color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:14px}
.about-cta p{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,15px);color:rgba(30,30,30,0.65);line-height:1.75;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 32px}
.btn-outline-light{border:1.5px solid rgba(30,30,30,0.4);color:var(--ink);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;padding:13px 30px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);display:inline-block;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.btn-outline-light:hover{border-color:var(--ink)}

@media(max-width:900px){.story-grid,.diff-grid,.founder-card{grid-template-columns:1fr}.pillar-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
@media(max-width:600px){.pillar-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.founder-card{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>

<script>
const observer = new IntersectionObserver(e => {
  e.forEach(t => { if(t.isIntersecting){ t.target.classList.add('visible'); observer.unobserve(t.target); }});
}, {threshold:0.1, rootMargin:'0px 0px -40px 0px'});
document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
